| TEST req isPow
| TAGS req user-function
|************************  
| in:  x:real[]
| out  y:bool[]
|------------------------
  isPowOf2(n) = 
        if(n==1)         true
        if(n>1 and n<2 ) false
        else isPowOf2(n/2)

  y = x.map(isPowOf2)          
        
|---------------------
| set x:[1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8,9]
| check y:[true,true,false,true,false,false,false,true,false]



